Package: soilgrids
Type: Package
Title: Manipulates soil grids data for easier 1AF use
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Matt Lowes
Maintainer: Matt Lowes <matt.lowes@oneacrefund.org>
Description: This package accesses saved soil grids data, trims down the values for speedy extracts,
    and extracts soil values for given GPS points. Future versions of the package will expand to working with 
    spatial polygons.
Imports: 
    sp (>= 1.3.1),
